nxi,\" playing Chu Qingge. She is a rapper, dancer, and singer.\n\nIn 2020, she joined iQiyi's survival show \"Youth with You\" and finished in 3rd place with 9,086,752 votes.\n\nOn May 30, 2020, she debuted with the final debut line of Youth With You girl group \"THE9.\"\n\nHer fandom name is \"Blackis\" and is under Shanghai Star 48 Culture Media.\n\nShe graduated from SNH48 Team SII on October 14, 2020.","name":"Xu Jiaqi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"許佳琪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"许佳琪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hứa Giai Kỳ","primary":false}}]}},"tv_233291_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774718575279,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/76Vdt31jeJtewbb5YkL1Q91DYeO.jpg","created_by":[],"episode_run_time":[],"first_air_date":"2026-03-25","genres":[{"id":16,"name":"Phim Hoạt Hình"},{"id":10759,"name":"Action & Adventure"}],"homepage":"","id":233291,"in_production":true,"languages":["zh"],"last_air_date":"2026-03-25","last_episode_to_air":{"id":7076363,"name":"Episode 3","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-03-25","episode_number":3,"episode_type":"standard","production_code":"","runtime":19,"season_number":1,"show_id":233291,"still_path":"/sPUxtEGtLUekxv5R7yktRevDRVx.jpg"},"name":"Sưu Thần Ký","next_episode_to_air":{"id":7076420,"name":"Episode 4","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-04-01","episode_number":4,"episode_type":"standard","production_code":"","runtime":null,"season_number":1,"show_id":233291,"still_path":null},"networks":[{"id":1330,"logo_path":"/fNxBFqWr7eWEgNeBDvvCxsSItXx.png","name":"iQiyi","origin_country":"CN"}],"number_of_episodes":24,"number_of_seasons":1,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","origi